Name: cJSON
Type: vendored third-party source
Upstream: https://github.com/DaveGamble/cJSON
Version: 1.7.19, as declared by cJSON.h
License: MIT

Files:
- cJSON.c
- cJSON.h

Use:
cJSON is compiled directly into cam_system for small JSON request and response
handling in the network command path.

Governance:
- Keep the upstream license header intact.
- Do not patch these files silently. If local changes become necessary, record
  them in docs/THIRD_PARTY_COMPONENTS.md and treat this directory as a fork.
- Recalculate file hashes after any update.
